Package com.code.aon.common.dao

Interface Summary
IDAO This interface allows CRUD operations about ITransferObject entities.
 

Class Summary
AliasWriter This class manages the generation of DAOConstantsEntry collections interface.
CriteriaUtilities Utilities for doing SQL statements.
DAOConstants This class manages bean metadata such as alias names.
DAOConstantsEntry This Class manages information of an IDAO constants stored in a file.
DAOConstantsReader This Class reads a XML constants file.
DAOConstantsResolver This Class manages operations of IDAO constants.
DAOConstantsWriter Writes field constants to a phisical file.
DAOFactory Factory of IDAO instances.
 

Exception Summary
DAOSysException The class DAOSysException indicates conditions created by a IDAO that a reasonable AON application might want to catch.
